ActAn Act respecting the mandatory reporting of Internet child pornography by persons who provide an Internet service
SubjectInternet Child Pornography Reporting Regulations
PrecisINTERNET CHILD PORNOGRAPHY REPORTING REGULATIONS in order to designate an organization for the purpose of receiving reports, and elaborate the role, functions and activities of that organization, and the manner in which those who provide Internet services to the public can discharge their obligations under the Act.
